document_data.mainbody:
'''''Chronomancer''''' is a 2{{nd}}-edition ''Advanced Dungeons & Dragons'' accessory.

{{Quote|''You have all the time in the world &ndash; and now you don't.''

''The final and most dangerous fantasy frontier lies not in space, but in time! At last, the dimension of Time is open to those few [[wizard]]s who would risk everything &ndash; even their very existence &ndash; to visit ancient and forgotten lands, or see the unbelievable wonders and horrors of the future. These few wizards are [[Chronomancer (class)|Chronomancers]], and this optional 96-page AD&amp;D game accessory reveals the secrets of their lives. New spells, new powers, and new realms &ndash; as well as terrifying monsters &ndash; are brought to light in this stunning work. Take time to study the mysteries of chronomancy &ndash; before someone else takes that time from you.''}}
